name: H5 Crew
message:
We wanted to sign your book late so Melania Trump couldn't steal our material!  Britt (2) and Matt, we are so excited for you!  What a beautiful day you have to look forward to, and a more beautiful stage in life to follow.  Although we haven't met Matt yet, there is no doubt of his love based on the M+B Story and the FB posts we enjoy seeing from all the way down here in Texas on the interweb thingy.  You two deserve the best!  And from what we KNOW about Brittney, and what we hear/see about Matt, the conclusion is clear.... you both found the best in each other!  Love you guys, can't wait to see you in November as husband and wife!
Britt (1) & Holly
